{"tid":302572,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大學競爭係好事黎","createTime":"2017-06-29T13:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T07:42:46.000Z","uid":36134,"like":110,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66acfac28e5bee1e69fea1f106ff35684a7889ba","tid":302572,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:10:44.000Z","msg":"平時唔多留意校園台<br />\n但作為舊登過黎<br />\n唔多唔少都知舊登同連登都多city hater<br />\n首先我唔係呢間大學既學生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近開個post問關於獸醫既野<br />\n見到唔少post都圍繞住排名 大學hater係度嘈<br />\n我習慣睇到d我覺得反智既行為<br />\n都要寫長文批判一下<br />\n真係唔係針對同做打手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得<br />\n競爭係一件好事黎 <br />\n如果永遠都係三大地位完全無可動搖<br />\n無人去沖擊 無人想去沖擊<br />\n佢地本身都會失去進步既動力壓力<br />\n所以我覺得部分刊衛三大價值既連登仔<br />\n為左佢地既三大價值不斷踩city既追排名行為<br />\n真係幾反智<br />\n情況就好似既得利益者害怕後來者居之<br />\n千方百計去打擊嘲笑對方<br />\n但好多連登仔都附和呢種想法"},{"pid":"ab011e0a439dae0fb11037c55241cd31ccecf6ff","tid":302572,"uid":36134,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"我認為香港辦學之所以咁好<br />\n年年都有進步<br />\n係因為有競爭<br />\n第一股競爭風氣由ust帶起<br />\n之後第二股係city帶動<br />\n<br />\n你話city刷排名無用<br />\n其實排名係幾重要既一項指標（影響到升學出國移民以至工作）<br />\n有d國家甚至以qs time作為佢地選擇移民既標準"},{"pid":"4762642160eb6885faf9dc385543de2ef4085ba5","tid":302572,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T18:04:39.000Z","msg":"agger 冇競爭冇進步"},{"pid":"a8e8ffabb28abd31e337b285ded0545baf306105","tid":302572,"uid":43717,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"都係大學攞筆錢出嚟請人坐同無謂裝修，city請人鳩坐，poly裝幾十部電視咪就係咁嚟，屌佢老未留筆錢派電腦送俾我好過啦"},{"pid":"d341731cdb7184cf1b4e3a8b819389e62c8d972a","tid":302572,"uid":36134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"仲有ust向上沖擊的成功經驗<br />\n令city有左參考既例子<br />\nCity既進取<br />\n連帶令到理浸呢d本來諗住安安份份過世既兩間院校<br />\n都開始作出唔少回應行動"},{"pid":"82aa73af94fd69e26cf2696ec2782ba1f1842605","tid":302572,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:22:47.000Z","msg":"大學競爭一向都係同全世界比<br />\n睇香港本地果幾間有乜好討論?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072a90dfec4f1a15e3f53425ea7d700d45c79258","tid":302572,"uid":36134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係大學攞筆錢出嚟請人坐同無謂裝修，city請人鳩坐，poly裝幾十部電視咪就係咁嚟，屌佢老未留筆錢派電腦送俾我好過啦</blockquote><br />\n咁你真係無知<br />\n大學要追排名<br />\n研究質素係好重要<br />\n尤其係科研方面<br />\n無可否認 ust同city係科研方面的確係好出色<br />\n成日都有研究發明上報紙<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢地係管理方面都好進取<br />\nUst大膽用美式學制<br />\nCity無懼阻礙開阻獸醫<br />\n其實都係唔想抱殘守缺既表現"},{"pid":"fc3a52511b5fdce7f5c080170f9c052b2b4e3be0","tid":302572,"uid":24224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:24:40.000Z","msg":"其實坦白講qs呢啲排名對香港搵工好似幫助唔會太大 但去外國就有用好多 好似我地要搵外國大學第一時間都係睇排名 因為根本唔知外國係點（佢地睇番我地香港都係一樣）"},{"pid":"fee83b8de9673cacfc9b0748e3cdc3c37ab65311","tid":302572,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學競爭一向都係同全世界比<br />\n睇香港本地果幾間有乜好討論?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本地幾間大學就好似同班同學<br />\n同一班點會無競爭？<br />\n一班既氛圍係好重要<br />\n你睇睇台灣就知競爭係幾咁重要"},{"pid":"92eacf3d36524f8af204ca962c818b5add69f3c5","tid":302572,"uid":99816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實坦白講qs呢啲排名對香港搵工好似幫助唔會太大 但去外國就有用好多 好似我地要搵外國大學第一時間都係睇排名 因為根本唔知外國係點（佢地睇番我地香港都係一樣）</blockquote><br />\noxbridge 勁d 定harvard勁？"},{"pid":"2f5c64365a4f2fb0f2b399e2c7a9a0759aa7fff6","tid":302572,"uid":24224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實坦白講qs呢啲排名對香港搵工好似幫助唔會太大 但去外國就有用好多 好似我地要搵外國大學第一時間都係睇排名 因為根本唔知外國係點（佢地睇番我地香港都係一樣）</blockquote><br />\noxbridge 勁d 定harvard勁？</blockquote><br />\n唔明巴打想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfe10321508985968e9759fbfb9cbad84ebeade","tid":302572,"uid":36134,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得連登仔應該糾正一下長久以來既歪風<br />\n見高就拜 見低就踩<br />\n努力上游既行為點都值得尊敬<br />\n抱殘守缺既想法一定要批判"},{"pid":"30a86e92ba8937b42f17f467097a5df12dcd7b95","tid":302572,"uid":2295,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得city就好似個努力既公屋仔<br />\n點努力都好 大家都好似唔太認同<br />\n有時仲比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5818166bada810d161dff303f9dc44e39150fc93","tid":302572,"uid":44593,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"取笑city仔 是因為自大的city仔沒有自知之明 以為自己並非垃圾"},{"pid":"13a0ceedaa3a93a735eadd45fa56f772d15738d2","tid":302572,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"連登仔乜燃都踩架la 佢地理撚得你好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b6fea609c338d64df335bfb22bc5e31624327b","tid":302572,"uid":14799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>取笑city仔 是因為自大的city仔沒有自知之明 以為自己並非垃圾</blockquote><br />\n食屎大學硬件老師的確係世界級<br />\n但一班食屎仔就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88025fe3687b1495b48f4f35fbedbeb7b94a188b","tid":302572,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有ust向上沖擊的成功經驗<br />\n令city有左參考既例子<br />\nCity既進取<br />\n連帶令到理浸呢d本來諗住安安份份過世既兩間院校<br />\n都開始作出唔少回應行動</blockquote><br />\n只計pg既話，ust應該超過左hku cu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7166db460170b51db1a9cf3e19adf5bb570e22bc","tid":302572,"uid":14799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有ust向上沖擊的成功經驗<br />\n令city有左參考既例子<br />\nCity既進取<br />\n連帶令到理浸呢d本來諗住安安份份過世既兩間院校<br />\n都開始作出唔少回應行動</blockquote><br />\n只計pg既話，ust應該超過左hku cu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUST MBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac0faed954679a971216d0510887675c738845e","tid":302572,"uid":85190,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"樓主可能無為意到 呢排臨近放榜 加上暑假<br />\n特別多有心人係呢個時間發功<br />\n多數就係DSE雞出黎擾敵加上少少其他U既玻璃心 <br />\n<br />\n不過睇佢地屌黎屌去都慣<br />\n講真 DSE要入邊間U既唔會因為連登仔屌兩句就真係唔入<br />\n亦都唔會話互屌輸佐就自卑<br />\n<br />\n本來唔會理果堆廢呻吟文 但難得見到樓主POST清泉文章 入黎支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2999db96d6d4012ac5b733ad04da62fcb259e7","tid":302572,"uid":28410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"競爭係好事黎<br />\n但要進步唔會係同本地其他非三大競爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec1a32fe732e299b607b70b7c35ab11bb70fc73","tid":302572,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有ust向上沖擊的成功經驗<br />\n令city有左參考既例子<br />\nCity既進取<br />\n連帶令到理浸呢d本來諗住安安份份過世既兩間院校<br />\n都開始作出唔少回應行動</blockquote><br />\n只計pg既話，ust應該超過左hku cu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇黎你眼中真係得MBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550c2c178e7abb8f4dbec7f4e919046e23a9f0fe","tid":302572,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有ust向上沖擊的成功經驗<br />\n令city有左參考既例子<br />\nCity既進取<br />\n連帶令到理浸呢d本來諗住安安份份過世既兩間院校<br />\n都開始作出唔少回應行動</blockquote><br />\n只計pg既話，ust應該超過左hku cu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUST MBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔只MBA, 其他Master program都好勁，D NDS都會將UST當做跳板， 不過phd 就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9945d12d30fe4552f5844a21739f3481dd1ddda",